      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI computed across three mesh levels (3.2M, 8.1M, 18.4M cells). GCI on the 8.1M production mesh is 1.8% for the volume-averaged hemolysis index, satisfying the acceptance criterion. Temporal discretization error assessed via time-step refinement; second-order convergence confirmed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
