      "rationale": "Experimental data from Morrison et al. (2012) covers flow rates of 2.5, 3.5, 5.0, 6.0, and 7.0 L/min at rotational speeds of 2500 and 3500 RPM. All 5 COU operating points are within 3% of tested conditions. Blood analog fluid properties documented and matched in CFD boundary conditions."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
