      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., NRMSE or mean absolute error) for RH index prediction must be below 15% across all validation operating points.",
      "rationale": "Normalized root-mean-square error for RH index prediction is 6.3% across all 5 validation operating points. Maximum single-point error is 11.2% at the 7.0 L/min, 3500 RPM condition. Achieved level exceeds required level due to consistent agreement across the full operating envelope, including the highest-hemolysis condition most relevant to worst-case identification."
    },
