      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index computed in validation experiments and CFD simulations is identical to the regulatory submission metric. No transformation or surrogate QoI is used. The RH < 1 criterion is directly applied to both validation comparisons and COU predictions, ensuring full QoI relevance."
    },
