      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection must be justified with reference to published validation data for rotating blood-contacting flows. Hemolysis damage accumulation model must be identified and referenced.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published performance for rotating machinery hemolysis CFD (Giersiepen power-law damage model). Model form justified by comparison of three turbulence model variants against experimental velocity data; SST k-omega showed lowest deviation. Hemolysis model coefficients sourced from Giersiepen et al. (1990) and confirmed applicable to the RH index formulation."
    },
    {
