      "rationale": "Inlet boundary conditions specified as fully developed pipe flow profiles computed from upstream geometry. Fluid properties (density 1056 kg/m3, dynamic viscosity 0.0035 Pa-s) sourced from published blood analog characterization. Rotational speed and flow rate boundary conditions set to nominal COU values. All inputs documented in the simulation input deck archived with this assessment."
