    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels at MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device with Medium model influence. CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for worst-case hemolysis identification across the full COU operating envelope. RH index predictions are within 11.2% of experimental values at all operating points, with all predicted values correctly ranking the worst-case condition. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the CPB use case.",
